Baby tanglefeet are located in the shady grove, which is located close to the Cosmic Altar in Zanaris. They are a weaker version of the Tanglefoot monster, which is fought during the A Fairy Tale Part I quest.

Baby tanglefeet have the trait of being invulnerable to all damage except magic secateurs, which is shared with the stronger Tanglefoot.
